Class Range

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Optimisable, Descriptive
    public class Range
extends PropertyHolder
implements Optimisable
    The actual physical range defined as a Segment with minimum and maximum values. This is used purely in context of the time sequence defined by the ExperimentalData.
